<UserControl
    x:Class="GetStartedApp.Views.Message"
    xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
    xmlns:d="http://schemas.microsoft.com/expression/blend/2008"
    xmlns:lay="clr-namespace:LayUI.Avalonia.Controls;assembly=LayUI.Avalonia"
    xmlns:mc="http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/markup-compatibility/2006"
    xmlns:prism="http://prismlibrary.com/"
    d:DesignHeight="450"
    d:DesignWidth="800"
    prism:ViewModelLocator.AutoWireViewModel="True"
    mc:Ignorable="d">
	<Border
        Margin="10"
        HorizontalAlignment="Center"
        VerticalAlignment="Center"
        BoxShadow="0 0 50 0 #3000"
        CornerRadius="2">
		<Grid MinWidth="300">
			<Grid.RowDefinitions>
				<RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
				<RowDefinition Height="10" />
				<RowDefinition Height="Auto" />
				<RowDefinition Height="*" />
			</Grid.RowDefinitions>
			<Border Grid.Row="0" Background="White" Padding="20">
				<Grid>
					<TextBlock
                        HorizontalAlignment="Center"
                        FontSize="24"
                        Foreground="Black"
                        Text="景区介绍" />
					<lay:LayButton
                        HorizontalAlignment="Right"
                        VerticalAlignment="Top"
                        Width="30"
                        Height="30"
                        Command="{Binding CloseCommand}"
                        Background="Transparent"
                        BorderThickness="0"
                        Foreground="Black"
                        Content="X"
                        FontSize="20"
                        Padding="0"
                        Margin="0">
						<lay:LayButton.Styles>
							<Style Selector="lay|LayButton:pointerover /template/ ContentPresenter">
								<Setter Property="Foreground" Value="Red" />
							</Style>
							<Style Selector="lay|LayButton:pressed /template/ ContentPresenter">
								<Setter Property="Foreground" Value="Red" />
							</Style>
						</lay:LayButton.Styles>
					</lay:LayButton>
				</Grid>
			</Border>
			<Border Grid.Row="1" Background="#F0F0F0" />
			<Border Grid.Row="2" Background="#F0F0F0" Padding="20,10">
				<TextBlock
                    FontSize="18"
                    Foreground="#FF9800"
                    Text="|景区详情" />
			</Border>
			<ScrollViewer Grid.Row="3" VerticalScrollBarVisibility="Auto" HorizontalScrollBarVisibility="Disabled">
				<Border Background="White" Padding="20,10">
					<StackPanel>
						<TextBlock
                            Foreground="Black"
                            TextWrapping="Wrap">
							禅达景区位于云南省腾冲县江苴村，是一个集自然风光、人文景观和宗教文化于一体的综合性旅游景区。景区内有丰富的植被和独特的地貌，吸引了大量游客前来观光。禅达景区以其宁静的环境和深厚的文化底蕴，成为了一个理想的休闲度假胜地。
						</TextBlock>
						<TextBlock
                            Margin="0,20,0,0"
                            Foreground="Black"
                            TextWrapping="Wrap">
							Chanda Scenic Area is located in Jiangzuo Village, Tengchong County, Yunnan Province. It is a comprehensive tourist attraction that integrates natural scenery, cultural landscapes, and religious culture. The area boasts rich vegetation and unique landforms, attracting a large number of tourists. With its tranquil environment and profound cultural heritage, Chanda Scenic Area has become an ideal destination for leisure and vacation.
						</TextBlock>
					</StackPanel>
				</Border>
			</ScrollViewer>
		</Grid>
	</Border>
</UserControl>